## Anthropic Harness Session Protocol

### Session Initialization Sequence

At the start of each coding session:

```bash
# 1. Confirm working directory
pwd
# Should be: /Users/anotonio.silva/antonio/theia-preview

# 2. Check git status
git status

# 3. Read progress file
cat features/theia-progress.txt

# 4. Select highest priority incomplete feature
cat features/feature-list.json | jq '[.categories[].features[] | select(.status == "failing")] | sort_by(.priority, .phase) | .[0]'
```

### Session End Protocol

Before ending each session:

```bash
# 1. Update feature status
# Edit features/feature-list.json - change status to "passing"

# 2. Log progress
echo "[$(date +%Y-%m-%d)] [Session N] - Implemented FEATURE-ID: Description" >> features/theia-progress.txt

# 3. Commit changes
git add .
git commit -m "feat(component): implement feature description"
```

