## Quick Reference Commands

| Task | Command/Prompt |
|------|----------------|
| Start session | Read `theia-progress.txt` + `feature-list.json` |
| Find next task | Filter failing features by priority |
| Implement feature | Follow TASKS.md story |
| Update status | Edit feature-list.json |
| Log progress | Append to theia-progress.txt |
| Commit | `git commit -m "type(scope): message"` |

---

## Conventional Commits

```
feat(scope): add new feature
fix(scope): fix bug
docs(scope): documentation changes
style(scope): formatting, no logic change
refactor(scope): code restructuring
test(scope): add/update tests
chore(scope): maintenance tasks
```

Scopes: `syntax`, `themes`, `editor`, `quicklook`, `settings`, `lsp`, `core`
